node.accessibility_caption: Photo by 𝓑𝓻𝓲𝓽𝓽𝓪𝓷𝔂 𝓞𝓼𝓴𝓮𝔂 in Sarasota, Florida. May be an image of 1 person, dog and outdoors.

node.text:
Her wings were ready, but our hearts were not! 🐕 🌈
.
.
Saying goodbye to my best friend after almost 13 years is the hardest thing I ever had to do. This past week and a half has been so hard watching her slowly get sicker and weaker. 
After talking to the vet,we knew the time had come to say goodbye to our girl ! 
.
Goodbyes are not forever
Goodbyes are not the end
They simply mean 
I’ll miss you until we meet again 
Rip Jewels! 
You will be missed more than you know! ❤️
